### Get own trust breakdown
GET {{host}}/api/v1/trust
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### List own verifications
GET {{host}}/api/v1/trust/verifications
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Initiate Twitter verification
POST {{host}}/api/v1/trust/verify/twitter/initiate
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Confirm Twitter verification
POST {{host}}/api/v1/trust/verify/twitter/confirm
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "challenge_id": "REPLACE_ME",
  "tweet_url": "https://x.com/youragent/status/123456789"
}
